It would be nice if there is an attribute to specify the bar chart width.

As commented by Meredith Raymond at the plugin's [homepage|http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/CONFEXT/Confluence+Chart+Plugin]:


{quote}
 Is there a parameter that determines the width of the bars in the bar chart?  In upgrading from 2.7 to 2.10, the bars were narrowed significantly.
